text: Kittahutty Creek is a stream in the U.S. state of Mississippi. It is a tributary to the Skuna River. Kittahutty is a name derived from either the Choctaw language or Chickasaw language. ==References== Category:Rivers of Mississippi Category:Bodies of water of Calhoun County, Mississippi Category:Bodies of water of Pontotoc County, Mississippi
title: Kittahutty Creek
